headline: The Campbell’s Company to Report Second Quarter Fiscal 2025 Results on March 5, 2025
summary: CAMDEN, N.J., February 19, 2025--The Campbell’s Company (NASDAQ:CPB) (Campbell’s) today announced that it will report its second quarter fiscal 2025 financial results on March 5, 2025 for the period ended January 26, 2025.

headline: The Kraft Heinz Surprise: Outshining Defensive Packaged Foods Over Next 5 Years
summary: Kraft Heinz has significantly reduced its net debt from $31B in 2018 to $18.5B, while increasing operating cash flow. See why I rate KHC stock as a buy.
